Program: The Forum
Title: Why Do we Need the State?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p033v73k
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 7 Oct 2015
Samira Ahmed is joined by World War Two historian Timothy Snyder who sees Hitler as the ultimate state destroyer, Belgian social policy researcher Benjamin Leruth who has been getting European citizens to be honest about what they really like and loathe about the EU, and writer Adrian Wooldridge who thinks authoritarian Singapore is a model for how to run an efficient state in the 21st Century. (Photo: Different flags of the world on flagpoles) Show less